The paper discusses the problem of analyzing firewall rule sets, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a method for simplifying firewall rule sets, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper uses formal methods to ensure that the simplification process preserves the semantics of the original rule set, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI).
